===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|weǵʰ}}
From {{inh|en|enm|weight}}, {{m|enm|weiȝte}}, {{m|enm|weght}}, {{m|enm|wight}}, from {{inh|en|ang|wiht}}, {{m|ang|ġewiht||weight}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*wihtiz}} {{gloss|"weight"; compare {{m|gem-pro|*weganą||to move}}}}, from {{inh|en|ine-pro|*weǵʰ-||to move; pull; draw; drive}}. 

