#*: "You surely are a man of some '''weight''' around here," I said.
# {{label|en|weightlifting}} A [[disc]] of [[iron]], [[dumbbell]], or [[barbell]] used for training the [[muscle]]s.
#: {{ux|en|He's working out with '''weights'''.}}
# {{label|en|physics}} [[mass|Mass]] ([[net weight]], [[atomic weight]], [[molecular weight]], [[troy weight]], [[carat weight]], etc.).
